      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a truly exceptional find? This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! From its flawless paint to its pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously cared for, making it a perfect choice for someone who demands the very best. It's rare to find a car this well-preserved\u2014come see it for yourself and experience perfection on wheels!",
