    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the factory. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, leaving the exterior paint with a flawless, mirror-like finish and no imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring leather upholstery that remains supple and free of any wear, alongside electronics that function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with all records available. A buyer can expect a showroom-quality vehicle that requires no immediate investment and offers a like-new driving experience.",
