    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including large dents, rusted panels, and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car requires major repairs to be roadworthy, as the engine runs roughly and there are several fluid leaks. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no guarantees on its performance or longevity.",
