    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go, but you\u2019re getting an absolute gem. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks just as good as the day I bought it! It\u2019s super clean, runs perfectly, and I\u2019ve kept up with everything to make sure it stays in tip-top condition. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
