    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defines 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic paint glow like glass. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine, smoke-free condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original factory textures are preserved throughout. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive folder of every service record since day one. You will find no door dings, no curb rash on the alloy wheels, and a spotless undercarriage. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 45800.0,
